<<declare $battleEnemy = "renee">>
<<set $reneeVisited=0>>
Renée Allard: Hold it right there, Bisclavret.
<<set $battleEnemy = "renee">>
Melion Bisclavret: Let me through, Renée. I need to–
Renée Allard: I know exactly what you need, Bisclavret, but I cannot allow it.
Renée Allard: You will not take more step towards that elevator.
Renée Allard: You will return to your desk, pick up your phone, and inform Mr. Tweed that you politely decline his offer and that Ms. Allard should be reinstated.
Melion Bisclavret: Renée, please–
Renée Allard: You will never have this role, Bisclavret. You aren't cut out for it. Not this century.
Renée Allard: Look around. Look at your clothes. It's like you can't even tell what year it is.
Renée Allard: You are an anachronism. This whole company is an anachronism. It's time for all of us to grow up.
Melion Bisclavret: That's not–
Renée Allard: You barely know how to send email. Poor LeThèque from IT booby trapped the printer to stop you from trying to 'fix' it.
Renée Allard: Face it, Bisclavret. *Someone* is trying to drag this place kicking and screaming into the new millennium. 
<<jump Renee_Challenge_Init>>
