__PrivCrochet_colorID: 8
__PrivCrochet_position: 137,442
__PrivCrochet_tags: 
title: Prologue
---
[Press 'Z' or 'SPACE' to begin.]

Once upon a time,
Back when foxes played polo,
And tigers used to smoke tobacco,
(Or wait, don't they still do that?)
There was a man named Melion.
Melion was a faithful servant to his lord.
He toiled each day in his lord's service.
His was a meager existence without recognition.
But one day, he recieved a message from above.
"Hey! Is this um... Melion Bisclavret?"
Melion Bisclavret: "This is he."
"Great! This is Marie-Luce, I'm calling from Mr. Tweed's office."
Marie-Luce: "Congratulations! You've been selected for a promotion to general manager."
Melion Bisclavret: "G–"
Marie-Luce: "If you could come up to sign a few papers to finalize the decision. You know, just protocol."
-> Of course!
    Melion Bisclavret: "Right, of course."
-> Not yet...
    Melion Bisclavret: "I need time to think about it."
Marie-Luce: "Well, be quick about it please. Mr. Tweed is a very busy man."
Melion Bisclavret: "Understood. I'll be there promptly."
Marie-Luce: "But if you'd like to celebrate a little with your co-workers on the way up, I won't stop you.
Marie-Luce: "I'm sure everyone'll want to congratulate you on the big accomplishment!"
-> Absolutely.
    Melion Bisclavret: "Sure, but am I not the first to hear of this?"
-> Absolutely not.
    Melion Bisclavret: "Uh... right. But you're saying I'm not the first to hear of this?"
Marie-Luce: "Well, not exactly. Gaurin found out and he's a bit of a gossip."
Melion Bisclavret:"Gaurin!?"
Marie-Luce: "Ha ha, you know him? He's–"
Melion Bisclavret: "I'll be right there. Goodbye."
*Click*
<<set $sceneEnd=1>>
===
